{
  "stem": "10859.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Push that in-- so many people in each house.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the-- we didn't have a place where to sleep for the-- we were sitting and sleeping.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And whatever somebody had that we brought with us-- like I said, when we-- to eat, we ate.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "You ate.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Whatever we didn't have, we didn't eat.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "A German officer used to take us out on the-- on the center of this little town.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And he used to talk to us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Don't you worry, he said.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We will take you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It's a war.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We will take you men out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "You have to work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "You have to do some work, because it's a [? war ?].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "The women and the children, we'll put it in in separate places.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And after the war, you'll be united-- just like that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Every morning, you used to come out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And I remember like today, even if it's more than 50 years.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "It was so hot-- miserable.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "In June, it's very hot that month, especially in Europe.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "It's very hot that month.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And we used to sweat, and stay hungry, not eating.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Were tired.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And he used to say-- and that's the way the language he used to use for the big lie every morning, for three days.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "I can tell you the feeling that everybody got after going out and staying, and being hungry, and not knowing what's gonna be the next hour, we already gave up life.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "We said, the hell with it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "It's not worth to fight it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Because that's the way you really get when you get so miserable.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And you get so help-- helpless.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And you cannot help yourself.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And you-- and you feel like you gonna fall down and you gonna die anyway.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
